VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \$\{(?!__frch_|index|item|foreach)[^}]+\}
WHEN EXPR MISSING:#\{|@Param|parameterType && MISSING:validate|sanitize
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects use of MyBatis ${} string substitution syntax in mapper XML files.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for String Substitution in MyBatis Mapper (${} Syntax).
